questionsAndAnswers.question: Do I provide a free demo for the website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I offer a free demo to give you a clear idea of the website’s design and functionality before finalizing the project. This ensures that the final product aligns with your vision and expectations.

questionsAndAnswers.question: I've got a WordPress website already. Is it possible to incorporate eCommerce functionality into it?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can give your current WordPress website eCommerce features.

questionsAndAnswers.question: can we discuss on project before order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, we can discuss on project. There are no charges for this.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will I set up the hosting and domain for your website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will set up the hosting and domain for your website. If needed, I can also assist in purchasing the hosting and domain on your behalf to make the process seamless for you.
